name: The Invisible Realm I Starseed One

metadata.name: Starseed One 1
metadata.description:
Starseed One is an AI-Collaborative project by The Invisible Realm. 
It chronicles the adventures of a diverse and intrepid set of interplanetary beings as they embark on social events, athletic contests, and search + rescue operations across the entire observable universe. As the AI endeavors to decipher intergalactic signals from a bygone era, transmitted via wormholes and gravitational fields that defy conventional laws of physics, some visual distortions or aberrations may be present.
